VERSION_TRACKING - ORIC-1 Emulator
=====================================

Current Version: 1.0.0-alpha
Release Date: 2026-02-22
Status: Feature Complete (Alpha)

Version History:
----------------
- 1.0.0-alpha (2026-02-22): All core subsystems implemented
  * Complete MOS 6502 CPU (151 opcodes, 13 addressing modes)
  * Memory system with ROM/RAM banking and I/O routing
  * MOS 6522 VIA with timers and interrupts
  * Keyboard matrix (8x8), cassette interface
  * Video system (text 40x28 + HIRES 240x200)
  * AY-3-8910 PSG audio (3 channels + noise + envelopes)
  * TAP cassette format support
  * Sedoric disk filesystem + FDC WD1793
  * Host filesystem sharing (HostFS + VFS)
  * Conversion tools (bas2tap, bin2tap, tap2sedoric)
  * Configuration system (.ini parser)
  * 136 unit/integration tests (100% pass)
  * Full emulation loop with I/O wiring

- 0.1.0-alpha (2026-01-31): Project initialization
  * Repository structure created
  * Initial architecture defined
  * Agile project management setup

Semantic Versioning:
-------------------
MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH-LABEL
- MAJOR: Incompatible API changes
- MINOR: New functionality (backward compatible)
- PATCH: Bug fixes (backward compatible)
- LABEL: alpha, beta, rc, stable

